'''Krokamargit''' is a [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[island]] belonging to the [[Piteå archipelago]]. The island is located in a bay (Margitviken) between Nötön and Renön,<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://kartor.eniro.se/?c=65.333805,21.591928&z=14&q=%2522Krokamargit%252034%2522;201718205;geo |title=Kartor, vägbeskrivningar, flygfoton, sjökort & mycket mer på eniro.se |website=kartor.eniro.se |access-date=2018-05-17}}</ref> where both islands have not yet permanently grown together further south. Krokamargit has no shore connection and there are some summer houses on it.

